  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bb5\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0b86\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Letter from the Prime Minister to the President regarding the appointment of the Governor of the Central Bank",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has recommended to President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa to reappoint Dr. Nannalal Weerasinghe as the Governor of the Central Bank.",
        "The Prime Minister has made this recommendation as the term of the Governor of the Central Bank comes to an end today.",
        "Finance Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has made this recommendation to the President as the recommendation of the Finance Minister is required if Dr. Nannalal Weerasinghe is to be re-appointed as the Governor of the Central Bank.",
        "The Prime Minister has recommended the appointment of Dr. Nannalal Weerasinghe as the Governor of the Central Bank of Sri Lanka for the next 6 years.",
        "Dr. Nannalal Weerasinghe became the Governor of the Central Bank within the last one or two months of the 6 year tenure of Dr. Indrajith Kumaraswamy, the former Governor of the Central Bank.",
        "Dr. Nannalal Weerasinghe has been appointed as the new Governor of the Central Bank by the President following the resignation of Ajit Nivard Cabral, the Governor of the Central Bank following the resignation of the Sri Lanka People's Front led Cabinet last April.",
        "Central Bank Governor Nannalal Weerasinghe has agreed to continue as governor and serve for six years.",
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has said that the Central Bank will never interfere in the activities of the Governor and top officials.",
        "Wrong economic decisions have led to an economic crisis and a political crisis that has caused massive problems in the country in the last one or two months.",
        "It was only after his appointment as Governor that Sri Lankans living abroad started sending money through the banking system.",
        "It is noteworthy that the removal of the Governor from the post when the issue is resolved will further intensify the hatred of the people against the government, so it is noteworthy that Sri Lanka People's Alliance MP Jagath Kumara has urged the President to create the conditions for him to continue as the Governor of the Central Bank."
      ],
